---
title: Sweet Chilli Glazed Chicken Thighs with Garlic-Ginger Rice & Stir-Fried Veggies
description: Every bite of this tasty meal is infused with flavour, from the steamed rice with garlic and ginger to the zesty stir-fried veggies and baked chicken with a sweet chilli glaze. Dive into a bowl of delicious delights!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dafea48c6da1c45702108c3-9c04ab40.jpg
